load/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/21_v3.mp3","time_start":58.05,"time_end":60.17},{"position":22,"content":"As long as you get there by 3:30, you should be fine.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/22_v3.mp3","time_start":60.17,"time_end":64.57},{"position":23,"content":"It's only 11 now, so plenty of time.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/23_v3.mp3","time_start":64.8,"time_end":67.63},{"position":24,"content":"Right.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/24_v3.mp3","time_start":67.63,"time_end":68.76},{"position":25,"content":"Do you need to buy vegetables too?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/25_v3.mp3","time_start":68.76,"time_end":71.24},{"position":26,"content":"I do, and I want to avoid all the plastic packaging in the supermarket!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/26_v3.mp3","time_start":71.24,"time_end":76.13},{"position":27,"content":"Well, there's a really nice organic shop there.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/27_v3.mp3","time_start":76.13,"time_end":79.53},{"position":28,"content":"Now what's it called...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/28_v3.mp3","time_start":79.76,"time_end":82.09},{"position":29,"content":"It's the name of a flower.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/29_v3.mp3","time_start":82.09,"time_end":84.29},{"position":30,"content":"I know, it's 'Rose'.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/30_v3.mp3","t