2.32},{"position":40,"content":"You can't miss it,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/40_v3.mp3","time_start":112.32,"time_end":113.67},{"position":41,"content":"there's also a big sign on the pavement so you can look for that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/41_v3.mp3","time_start":113.67,"time_end":119.04},{"position":42,"content":"Fine!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/42_v3.mp3","time_start":119.04,"time_end":120.19},{"position":43,"content":"I guess if I need anything else, I'll have to go to the supermarket.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/43_v3.mp3","time_start":120.69,"time_end":124.84},{"position":44,"content":"Yeah, you should be able to get everything you need,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/44_v3.mp3","time_start":124.84,"time_end":128.73},{"position":45,"content":"but there's a minibus that goes to the supermarket if you need it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/45_v3.mp3","time_start":128.73,"time_end":133.09},{"position":46,"content":"It's purple and the number is 289.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/46_v3.mp3","time_start":133.09,"time_end":137.2},{"position":47,"content":"Thanks, that's great.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/47_v3.mp3","time_start":137.2,"time_end":139.72},{"position":48,"content":"So what do you need to get at the fish market?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/48_v3.mp3","time_start":140.19,"time_end":143.57},{"position":49,"content":"The salmon is always very good and the shellfish...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/49_v3.mp3","time_start":143.57,"time_end":147.57},{"position":50,"content":"I'm going to make a curry, I think,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/50_v3.mp3","time_start":147.57,"time_end":150.23},{"position":51,"content":"and I need about 12 prawns for that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/51_v3.mp3","time_start":150.23,"time_end":153.2},{"position":52,"content":"They'll have plenty of those.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/52_v3.mp3","time_start":153.2,"time_end":155.48},{"position":53,"content":"Have you ever tried samphire?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/53_v3.mp3","time_start":155.75,"time_end":158.16},{"position":54,"content":"No, what's that?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/54_v3.mp3","time_start":158.16,"time_end":160.12},{"position":55,"content":"It's a type of seaweed.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/55_v3.mp3","time_start":160.12,"time_end":162.89},{"position":56,"content":"I just ask for a handful and you fry it in butter.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/56_v3.mp3","time_start":162.89,"time_end":166.96},{"position":57,"content":"It's delicious!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/57_v3.mp3","time_start":166.96,"time_end":168.03},{"position":58,"content":"Oh, I might try that,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/58_v3.mp3","time_start":168.03,"time_end":170.48},{"position":59,"content":"how do you spell it?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/59_v3.mp3","time_start":170.48,"time_end":171.99},{"position":60,"content":"It's SAMPHIRE.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/60_v3.mp3","time_start":171.99,"time_end":181.73},{"position":61,"content":"Great! It's always good to try something different.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/61_v3.mp3","time_start":181.73,"time_end":186.07},{"position":62,"content":"I'll see what beans they have in the organic shop","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/62_v3.mp3","time_start":186.25,"time_end":189.97},{"position":63,"content":"and I think I'll get something for dessert there.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/63_v3.mp3","time_start":189.97,"time_end":193.39},{"position":64,"content":"How about a mango?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/64_v3.mp3","time_start":193.39,"time_end":195.35},{"position":65,"content":"I'm not sure, they're not always ripe.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/65-2024-07-09-11-37-51.mp3","time_start":195.35,"time_end":199.2},{"position":66,"content":"I'd prefer a melon, it's bigger too.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/66_v3.mp3","time_start":199.12,"time_end":202.25},{"position":67,"content":"Good idea.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/67_v3.mp3","time_start":202.25,"time_end":203.64},{"position":68,"content":"The owner also sells a lot of spices there that you can put in a curry,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/68_v3.mp3","time_start":203.64,"time_end":209.56},{"position":69,"content":"and things like coconut.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/69_v3.mp3","time_start":209.56,"time_end":211.77},{"position":70,"content":"Oh, that's very helpful.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/70_v3.mp3","time_start":211.77,"time_end":213.87},{"position":71,"content":"I'll have a look.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/71_v3.mp3","time_start":213.87,"time_end":215.11},{"position":72,"content":"No problem.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/72_v3.mp3","time_start":215.11,"time_end":216.24},{"position":73,"content":"I know bread doesn't really go with curry","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/73_v3.mp3","time_start":216.24,"time_end":219.56},{"position":74,"content":"but I always like to have some in case.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/74_v3.mp3","time_start":219.56,"time_end":222.35},{"position":75,"content":"As I said, all the bread is home-made and there's lots of variety.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/75_v3.mp3","time_start":222.35,"time_end":227.71},{"position":76,"content":"I like the brown bread myself.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/76_v3.mp3","time_start":227.71,"time_end":229.87},{"position":77,"content":"Mm, sounds good.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/77_v3.mp3","time_start":229.87,"time_end":231.84},{"position":78,"content":"They sell other things there too.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/78_v3.mp3","time_start":231.84,"time_end":234.11},{"position":79,"content":"Like cakes?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/79_v3.mp3","time_start":234.11,"time_end":235.52},{"position":80,"content":"I love chocolate cake.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/80_v3.mp3","time_start":235.88,"time_end":237.88},{"position":81,"content":"Well, not that,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/81_v3.mp3","time_start":237.88,"time_end":239.85},{"position":82,"content":"but they have a whole range of tarts","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/82_v3.mp3","time_start":239.85,"time_end":242.89},{"position":83,"content":"and the best are the strawberry ones.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/83_v3.mp3","time_start":242.89,"time_end":246.48},{"position":84,"content":"Perfect!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/84_v3.mp3","time_start":246.48,"time_end":247.67},{"position":85,"content":"Hopefully I won't even have to go to the supermarket!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/cam19-test-3-part-1-2024-06-22-00-23-25/85_v3.mp3","time_start":247.67,"time_end":251.48}]}